					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
					<label class="control-label">
						<div class="notes notes-primary">
							<p>Textarea with Auto Resize</p>
							<p><a href="http://www.technoreply.com/autogrow-textarea-plugin-3-0/" target="_blank">Autogrow textarea plugin</a> makes it easy to create text area auto resize.</p>
						</div>
